52Fnectar-vs-casper-mattress-comparison%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nectarsleep.com%252Fp%252Fwarranty-policy%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforever%20warranty%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20mattresses.%20However%2C%20its%20warranty%20does%20have%20caveats%2C%20including%20that%20it's%20only%20valid%20for%20the%20original%20purchaser%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20void%20if%20the%20cover%20has%20been%20removed.%20If%20the%20mattress%20is%20more%20than%2010%20years%20old%2C%20Nectar%20has%20the%20option%20to%20just%20repair%20(not%20replace)%20it%20and%20charge%20you%20shipping%20both%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Nectar%20has%20a%20more%20extensive%20trial%20period%2C%20Casper%20has%20a%20more%20straightforward%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%20process%20compared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20Casper%20mattress%20boxes%20are%20displayed%20inside%20near%20the%20front%20door%20of%20a%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a83bffdcdb354a9858612f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20you%20order%20a%20mattress%20(or%20four)%2C%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20home%20compressed%20in%20a%20box%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mini%20fridge.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Casper%20and%20Nectar%20are%20bed-in-a-box%20companies%20and%20arrive%20at%20your%20doorstep%20in%20a%20large%20box.%20From%20there%20you%20need%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20plastic%20and%20wait%20for%20the%20mattress%20to%20expand%20to%20its%20full%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20both%20setup%20processes%20are%20pretty%20similar.%20As%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20a%20heavier%20mattress%20is%20usually%20more%20difficult%20to%20set%20up%2C%20hence%20why%20size%20matters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Casper%20and%20Nectar%20offer%20at-home%20assembly%20services%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Glove%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BPremium%20In-Home%20Set%20Up%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20you%20get%20your%20new%20mattress%20up%20and%20running%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20your%20old%20one.%20Nectar's%20at-home%20setup%20costs%20%24199%20whereas%20Casper's%20is%20%24149.%20You'll%20save%20a%20bit%20of%20money%20with%20Casper%2C%20but%20they%20are%20relatively%20close%20in%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20brands%20note%20that%20it%20takes%20between%2024%20and%2072%C2%A0%20hours%20for%20the%20mattress%20to%20fully%20expand.%20That%20said%2C%20after%2010%20hours%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20both%20mattresses%20were%20fully%20expanded%2C%20and%20the%20chemical-like%20smell%20from%20the%20Nectar%20mattress%20had%20dissipated%3B%20it%20was%20even%20longer%20for%20the%20Casper%20One.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETie%3B%20Nectar%20and%20Casper%20both%20have%20an%20easy%20setup%20process%20with%20the%20bed-in-a-box%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfort%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%20compared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EComfort%20is%20key%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20mattress.%20A%20few%20factors%20determine%20comfort%20%E2%80%94%20pressure%20relief%2C%20cooling%20properties%2C%20and%20firmness.%20The%20Nectar%20mattress%20and%20Casper%20One%20are%20medium-firm%20and%20help%20promote%20spinal%20alignment%20and%20pressure%20relief%20for%20a%20comfortable%20night's%20sleep%20for%20back%2C%20side%2C%20and%20stomach%20sleepers.%20We%20were%20most%20comfortable%20sleeping%20on%20our%20sides%20with%20the%20Nectar%20mattress%2C%20but%20any%20position%20was%20still%20pretty%20good.%20For%20Casper%2C%20we%20preferred%20sleeping%20on%20our%20stomachs%2C%20and%20it's%20also%20well-suited%20for%20back%20sleepers.%20Side%20sleepers%20may%20find%20it%20too%20firm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20element%20of%20comfort%20is%20breathability.%20The%20Casper%20One%20mattress%20is%20highly%20breathable%2C%20making%20it%20comfortable%20for%20hot%20sleepers%2C%20whereas%20the%20Nectar%20is%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20so%20you're%20not%20left%20constantly%20twisting%20and%20turning%20during%20the%20night.%20This%20is%20a%20great%20feature%20for%20those%20who%20live%20in%20warm%20climates%20or%20run%20on%20the%20hot%20side%20and%20need%20any%20temperature%20regulation%20they%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Tossup%3B%20depends%20on%20individual%20preferences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Heat%20dissipation%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20dissipation%20compared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20worse%20than%20waking%20up%20in%20a%20puddle%20of%20sweat%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20Luckily%2C%20both%20Casper%20and%20Nectar's%20mattresses%20can%20dissipate%20heat%20well%20enough%20to%20keep%20you%20more%20comfortable%20and%20help%20regulate%20body%20temperature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20sleep%20cooler%20with%20the%20Casper%20lineup%2C%20The%20Casper%20Snow%20is%20the%20most%20recommended%20option%20for%20hot%20sleepers%3B%20it%20uses%20a%20phase-change%20material%20(PCM)%20to%20keep%20you%20cool%20during%20the%20night%20on%20its%20top%20layer.%20The%20One%20has%20a%20cozy%20knit%20layer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20noticed%20that%20Nectar's%20mattresses%20are%20great%20at%20dissipating%20heat%3B%20dropping%20more%20than%2015%20degrees%20during%20one%20of%20our%20tests.%20One%20night%20we%20even%20had%20to%20add%20an%20extra%20blanket%20because%20it%20was%20so%20cooling.%20The%20Nectar%20uses%20gel%20foam%20and%20its%20cover%20uses%20heat-absorbent%20polyethylene%20fibers%20to%20help%20you%20sleep%20cooler.%20However%2C%20the%20Casper%20just%20narrowly%20edged%20out%20the%20Nectar%20regarding%20heat%20dissipation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECasper%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Edge%20support%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEdge%20support%20compared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221541%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20sitting%20on%20the%20Nectar%20Mattress%20holds%20a%20yardstick%20next%20to%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642c5864d335200018dd95a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20measure%20edge%20support%20by%20examining%20how%20much%20the%20edges%20sink%20with%20a%20yard%20stick.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20support%20ensures%20that%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20mattress%20don't%20sink%20when%20pressure%20is%20applied.%20We%20felt%20fully%20supported%20on%20our%20Nectar%20mattress%20and%20had%20to%20roll%20quite%20far%20to%20the%20side%20before%20actually%20falling%20off%20the%20bed.%20When%20measured%20with%20a%20ruler%2C%20it%20also%20sank%203%20inches%20which%20is%20less%20than%203.5%20inches%20from%20other%20mattresses%20we've%20tested%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20we%20noticed%20Casper%20mattresses%20had%20less%20sturdy%20edge%20support%20and%20experienced%20more%20significant%20sagging.%20This%20wasn't%20anything%20too%20crazy%2C%20and%20you%20won't%20feel%20like%20you're%20going%20to%20roll%20off.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20more%20than%20the%20Nectar%2C%20for%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Nectar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Motion%20transfer%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20transfer%20compared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20drops%20a%20bowling%20ball%20on%20the%20Nectar%20Mattress%2C%20where%20a%20can%20of%20beer%20is%20resting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e68f0696242f0019e86535%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20soda%20can%20didn't%20tip%20over%20on%20the%20Nectar%20mattress%20when%20we%20dropped%20a%20bowling%20ball%20onto%20the%20bed%20just%20a%20foot%20away.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMotion%20isolation%20is%20important%20for%20couples%20who%20might%20share%20the%20same%20bed%20as%20small%20movements%20may%20be%20felt%20by%20the%20other%20person%20during%20the%20night.%20We%20tested%20the%20motion%20isolation%20by%20dropping%20a%20bowling%20ball%20four%20feet%20from%20the%20air%20and%20observed%20whether%20it%20knocked%20over%20a%20soda%20can.%20For%20both%20the%20Nectar%20and%20the%20Casper%20mattresses%2C%20the%20can%20didn't%20tip%20when%20we%20dropped%20the%20ball%2C%20both%20exhibiting%20minimal%20motion%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Tie%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Nectar%20and%20Casper%20offer%20bed-in-a-box%20options%20for%20different%20types%20of%20sleepers%20at%20a%20variety%20of%20price%20points.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20the%20Nectar%20mattress%20and%20the%20Casper%20One%2C%20the%20Nectar%20is%20better%20overall%2C%20with%20sturdy%20edge%20support%2C%20easy%20set-up%2C%20and%20a%20more%20affordable%20price%20point.%20That%20said%2C%20hot%20sleepers%20might%20prefer%20using%20a%20Casper%20because%20of%20how%20well%20the%20heat%20dissipates%20through%20the%20memory%20foam%20layers.%20Nectar%20will%20also%20be%20a%20better%20choice%20for%20side%20and%20back%20sleepers%2C%20while%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers%20will%20find%20more%20support%20with%