.%20I%20can%20only%20assume%20that%20Dara%20is%20unaware%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ackman%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20demanded%20that%20Uber%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20return%20the%20stolen%20funds%20with%20interest%20to%20the%20NYC%20taxi%20drivers%20and%20to%20other%20drivers%20in%20any%20other%20markets%20where%20they%20are%20doing%20the%20same%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bshould%20deeply%20apologize%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20called%20on%20Uber%20to%20%26quot%3Brestate%20its%20earnings%20to%20reflect%20this%20overstatement%20of%20margins%20and%20profits.%26quot%3B%20He%20then%20tagged%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20in%20the%20post%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20he%20agrees%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUber%20was%20quick%20to%20react%20to%20Mr%20Ackman's%20accusations.%20Responding%20to%20his%20post%2C%20Uber's%20communications%20team%20clarified%20that%20the%20company%20passes%20100%25%20of%20the%20tip%20to%20their%20taxi%20partners%20%26quot%3Band%20they%20are%20required%20to%20pass%20the%20tip%20to%20the%20driver%2C%20usually%20within%20a%20day%20or%20so%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tip%20isn't%20showing%20on%20this%20screen%20because%20passengers%20tip%20after%20the%20trip%20ends%2C%20and%20this%20screen%20doesn't%20refresh.%20That's%20why%20the%20screen%20says%20'tip%20may%20be%20added%20by%20passenger%20after%20trip%20completion'%20and%20'check%20trip%20history%20for%20final%20Grand%20Total%20amount%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHi%20Bill%20-%20we're%20stepping%20in%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdkhos%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40dkhos%3C%2Fa%3E%20who's%20on%20a%20business%20trip.%20We%20pass%20100%25%20of%20the%20tip%20to%20Curb%20(our%20taxi%20partner)%2C%20and%20they%20are%20required%20to%20pass%20the%20tip%20to%20the%20driver%2C%20usually%20within%20a%20day%20or%20so.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20tip%20isn't%20showing%20on%20this%20screen%20because%20passengers%20tip%20after%20the%20trip%20ends%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Uber%20Comms%20(%40Uber_Comms)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUber_Comms%2Fstatus%2F1793505257659736074%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20as%20clear%20as%20it%20should%20be%20for%20taxi%20drivers%2C%26quot%3B%20Uber%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20relatively%20new%20product%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we'll%20work%20with%20our%20partners%20to%20improve%20this%20screen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ackman%20then%20thanked%20Uber%20for%20the%20clarification%2C%20but%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20said%2C%20I%20paid%20the%20tip%20first%20and%20then%20the%20driver's%20screen%20that%20I%20photographed%20appeared%20afterwards.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20drivers%20definitely%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20not%20being%20paid%20and%20they%20have%20no%20ability%20to%20audit%20whether%20the%20passenger%20has%20paid%20a%20tip%20or%20not.%20This%20seems%20like%20an%20easy%20problem%20to%20fix%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthought-it-was-cool-zerodhas-nikhil-kamath-reveals-he-wanted-to-adopt-a-child-5742900%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThought%20It%20Was%20Cool%26quot%3B%3A%20Zerodha's%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20Reveals%20He%20Wanted%20To%20Adopt%20A%20Child%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdkhos%2Fstatus%2F1793631615069081709%5C%22%3EMr%20Khosrowshahi%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20responded%20to%20Mr%20Ackman%2C%20writing%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Uber%20taxi%20pilot%20was%20%26quot%3Bstill%20in%20test%2Flearn%20mode%26quot%3B%