p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B400%20paar%20(crossing%20400)%20was%20not%20just%20our%20campaign%20slogan%2C%20but%20our%20resolve.%20After%20six%20phases%2C%20we%20are%20very%20confident%20of%20crossing%20that%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20told%20NDTV%20on%20May%2012%20during%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Bihar%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20expand%20its%20footprint%20hugely%20in%20eastern%20India%20this%20time%2C%20which%20would%20take%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20easily%20over%20the%20400-seat%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20visited%20almost%20all%20the%20states%20of%20India.%20And%20I%20can%20say%20that%20Bihar%20has%20added%20many%20colours%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20NDA's%20resolution%20of%20'400%20paar'.%20The%20atmosphere%20in%20Bihar%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20entire%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20contested%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lucknow%20constituency%20this%20time%20again.%20He%20had%20won%20from%20there%20twice.%20Lucknow%20is%20a%20prestigious%20seat%20previously%20represented%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20retained%20power%20in%202019%2C%20with%20an%20even%20larger%20seat%20share%20than%20in%202014.%20Mr%20Singh%20remained%20one%20of%20the%20key%20members%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20cabinet%20and%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20Defence%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20in%20mind%20the%20spirit%20of%20'Make%20in%20India'%20and%20'Aatmanirbhar%20Bharat'%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20banned%20the%20import%20of%20101%20defence-related%20items%20in%202020.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20108%20military%20weapons%20and%20systems%2C%20including%20next-generation%20corvettes%2C%20airborne%20early%20warning%20systems%2C%20tank%20engines%20and%20radars%20would%20be%20entirely%20made%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E