at-to-know-before-group-fitness-class-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20to%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20extremely%20relaxed%2C%20my%20limbs%20felt%20like%20jelly%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fhot-yoga%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20mood%20improved%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Maybe%20it's%20because%20I%20mainly%20took%20classes%20at%20night%20when%20the%20workday%20ended%2C%20but%20I%20always%20slept%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20difference%20was%20really%20noticeable%20during%20a%20stressful%20period%20at%20work%2C%20and%20my%20body%20started%20to%20crave%20the%20hot-yoga%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db5683da-0f97-44c5-8ffc-4f92677c7fe1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20expect%20it%2C%20but%20hot%20yoga%20also%20seemed%20to%20affect%20my%20skin%20and%20hair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223590%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20stands%20on%20a%20black%20yoga%20mat%20and%20crouches%20down%20with%20right%20arm%20outstretched%20toward%20the%20ceiling%20and%20left%20arm%20toward%20the%20ground%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6628274323b29110d3022443%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222693%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20heat%20and%20humidity%20in%20the%20hot-yoga%20classes%20impacted%20my%20skin%20and%20hair.%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20prone%20to%20blackheads%20and%20clogged%20pores%2C%20but%20as%20I%20attended%20the%20classes%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20my%20complexion%20became%20clearer%20and%20my%20skin%20looked%20plumper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanctuarymedical.com%2Fprovider%2Fdr-azza-halim%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Azza%20Halim%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20board-certified%20anesthesiologist%20and%20physician%20who%20focuses%20on%20aesthetic%20medicine%2C%20antiaging%20treatments%2C%20and%20regenerative%20medicine%2C%20doing%20hot%20yoga%20may%20have%20helped%20my%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHot%20yoga%20indirectly%20benefits%20the%20skin%20by%20improving%20overall%20circulation%2C%20which%20allows%20oxygen%20and%20nutrients%20to%20flow%20to%20the%20skin%20cells%2C%20promoting%20collagen%20production%20and%20helping%20to%20maintain%20elasticity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20doctor%2C%20heat%20can%20help%20open%20up%20pores%20and%20flush%20out%20toxins.%20However%2C%20sweat%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20bacteria%20left%20on%20the%20skin%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20acne.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20important%20to%20cleanse%20the%20skin%20thoroughly%20after%20a%20hot-yoga%20session%20to%20remove%20any%20sweat%20or%20impurities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20think%20my%20hair%20suffered%20while%20doing%20hot%20yoga%20every%20day%2C%20and%20my%20hairstylist%20even%20commented%20on%20how%20dry%20and%20frizzy%20my%20hair%20was%20when%20I%20showed%20up%20for%20my%20haircut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Halim%20said%20my%20dry%2C%20frizzy%20hair%20could%20be%20due%20to%20the%20combination%20of%20heat%20and%20daily%20showering%20after%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22004e7956-0cf6-43ef-98a3-2bf5d5cb278f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20hydrated%20seemed%20to%20help%20my%20success%20in%20hot-yoga%20classes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20stands%20in%20a%20one-legged%20pose%20with%20her%20arms%20above%20her%20head%20and%20smiles%20in%20a%20yoga%20studio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6628291f10dfcda409627721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20felt%20better%20during%20classes%20on%20days%20when%20I%20had%20plenty%20of%20water.%3Cp%3ELara%20Walsh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20month%2C%20I%20realized%20hot-yoga%20classes%20were%20significantly%20tougher%20for%20me%20when%20I%20hadn't%20had%20enough%20water%20or%20was%20hungover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fplantbasedboxer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKollins%20Ezekh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20personal%20trainer%20and%20celebrity%20fitness%20instructor%2C%20dehydration%20can%20definitely%20make%20a%20workout%20more%20difficult.%20The%20expert%20said%20not%20drinking%20enough%20water%20can%20significantly%20impact%20performance%2C%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20you%20feel%20dizzy%2C%20weak%2C%20and%20even%20causing%20cramping.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20adding%20electrolytes%20to%20my%20beverages%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20having%20a%20cup%20of%20water%20before%20my%20morning%20coffee%2C%20which%20gave%20me%20more%20energy%20for%20class%20and%20taught%20me%20the%20importance%20of%20listening%20to%20my%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b1c8810-bde9-4030-a667-aa608d94138f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20seemed%20like%20hot%20yoga%20toned%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20fit%20into%20old%20clothes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20few%20classes%2C%20my%20arms%20and%20legs%20shook%20even%20when%20I%20exercised%20with%20light%20weights.%20But%20eventually%2C%20despite%20putting%20in%20minimal%20effort%20in%20some%20classes%2C%20I%20saw%20my%20arms%2C%20abs%2C%20waist%2C%20and%20back%20become%20more%20toned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%2C%20I%20graduated%20from%205-pound%20to%208-pound%20weights%20for%20leg%20exercises.%20Moves%20like%20chaturanga%20dandasana%20(a%20low%20plank)%2C%20downward%20dog%2C%20and%20cobra%20also%20helped%20strengthen%20my%20upper%20body%2C%20back%2C%20and%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20how%20much%20weight%20I%20had%20lost%20until%20I%20fit%20into%20a%20dress%20and%20a%20top%20that%20I%20hadn't%20been