29b38cb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoters-fear-trump-refuse-leave-office-when-term-ends-report-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anxiety%20appears%20to%20building%20among%20some%20voters%20over%20Trump's%20often%20charged%2C%20authoritarian%20rhetoric%20and%20incidents%20such%20as%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%20riot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nrennolds%40insider.com%20(Nathan%20Rennolds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvoters-fear-trump-refuse-leave-office-when-term-ends-report-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Do%20Aliens%20Exist%3F%20Are%20We%20Alone%3F%20Here's%20What%20We%20Know%20So%20Far%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20extraterrestrial%20life%20has%20always%20fascinated%20humans%20and%20we've%20been%20searching%20for%20alien%20life%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20However%2C%20despite%20decades%20of%20peering%20at%20and%20listening%20to%20planets%20around%20other%20stars%2C%20we%20still%20don't%20have%20a%20concrete%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20we%20are%20alone%20in%20the%20universe.%20But%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%20of%20life%20beyond%20our%20planet%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20doesn't%20exist.%20The%20more%20we%20learn%20about%20the%20Cosmos%20-%20from%20the%20planets%20and%20moons%20in%20our%20Solar%20System%20to%20the%20great%20expanse%20beyond%20-%20the%20more%20confident%20people%20have%20become%20that%20alien%20life%20must%20be%20out%20there.%20Now%2C%20here's%20what%20scientists%20say%20about%20the%20biggest%20questions%20people%20might%20have%20about%20what%20kind%20of%20life%20is%20most%20likely%20to%20actually%20be%20out%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20likely%20is%20it%20that%20alien%20life%20exists%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20currently%20isn't%20any%20evidence%20of%20life%20on%20other%20planets%2C%20but%20the%20universe%20is%20a%20big%20place%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20that%20out%20of%20the%20trillions%20of%20planets%20that%20are%20presumed%20to%20exist%20in%20our%2013.8%20billion-year-old%20universe%2C%20only%20Earth%20has%20ever%20hosted%20life.%20Thus%2C%20the%20search%20for%20extraterrestrial%20life%20is%20a%20serious%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20efforts%20in%20the%20search%20for%20extraterrestrial%20life%20started%20well%20before%20humans%20had%20the%20capacity%20to%20get%20off%20our%20own%20planet.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20240308-how-the-hunt-for-alien-life-is-hotting-up%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20early%20attempts%20to%20search%20for%20extraterrestrial%20intelligence%2C%20called%20Seti%2C%20began%20in%20the%20mid-20th%20Century%2C%20with%20astronomers%20looking%20in%20vain%20for%20radio%20signals%20on%20other%20planets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20military%20pilots%20in%20the%20US%20have%20seen%20things%20that%20look%20otherworldly.%20The%20Pentagon%20has%20established%20an%20office%20to%20look%20into%20the%20sightings.%20US%20Congress%20has%20heard%20hearings.%20Moreover%2C%20UFOs%20were%20rebranded.%20Unidentified%20flying%20objects%20are%20now%2C%20per%20the%20US%20government%20edict%2C%20unidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena%20(UAPs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20our%20galaxy%20has%20been%20studied%20and%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20aliens%20exist%20is%20something%20scientists%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20understand%2C%20explore%20and%20figure%20out%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20All%20possibilities%20remain%20in%20play.%20Including%20the%20possibility%20that%20we%20are%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20we%20might%20find%20aliens%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20possible%20that%20there%20is%20alien%20life%20within%20our%20solar%20system.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20everything%20we've%20learnt%20about%20Mars%20suggests%20that%20its%20formation%20and%20evolution%20are%20comparable%20to%20Earth%20and%20that%20the%20planet%20was%20once%20quite%20capable%20of%20hosting%20ecosystems.%20NASA%20believes%20that%20exploration%20of%20Mars%20could%20uncover%20evidence%20of%20life%20and%20answer%20one%20of%20the%20fundamental%20mysteries%20of%20the%20cosmos%3A%20Does%20life%20exist%20beyond%20Earth%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetary.org%2Farticles%2Fare-aliens-real%5C%22%3EPlanetary%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20moons%20of%20Jupiter%20and%20Saturn%20also%20have%20the%20potential%20of%20hosting%20alien%20life%2C%20since%20many%20of%20them%20have%20liquid%20water%20under%20their%20icy%20crusts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20field%20of%20exoplanet%20research%20is%20yielding%20new%20possibilities%20for%20life%20beyond%20our%20Solar%20System.%20We%20now%20know%20of%20more%20than%205%2C500%20planets%20around%20other%20stars%2C%20known%20as%20exoplanets%2C%20and%20more%20continue%20to%20trickle%20in%20every%20day.%20With%20the%20immense%20power%20of%20new%20telescopes%2C%20most%20notably%20the%20James%20Webb%20Space%20Telescope%20(JWST)%2C%20astronomers%20are%20now%20beginning%20to%20probe%20some%20of%20these%20planets%20in%20exquisite%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20as%20we%20discover%20planets%20in%20other%20star%20systems%2C%20we%20can%20also%20look%20at%20the%20atmosphere%20for%20biosignatures%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20listen%20for%20signs%20of%20alien%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20UFOs%20or%20UAPs%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnidentified%20flying%20objects%20(UFOs)%2C%20now%20more%20commonly%20known%20as%20unidentified%20aerial%20phenomena%20(UAPs)%2C%20have%20captured%20people's%20imaginations%20for%20generations.%20They%20are%20catch-all%20terms%20to%20describe%20objects%20detected%20in%20the%20air%2C%20sea%20and%20space%20that%20defy%20easy%20explanations.%20Many%20believe%20that%20aliens%20are%20responsible%20for%20UFO%20and%20UAP%20sightings%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20concrete%20evidence%20to%20support%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20definition%2C%20UFOs%20and%20UAPs%20are%20just%20things%20that%20aren't%20identifiable.%20There%20is%20a%20widespread%20belief%20that%20aliens%20regularly%20visit%20our%20planet.%20Hundreds%20of%20military%20and%20commercial%20pilots%20have%20reported%20UAP%20encounters.%20The%20Pentagon%20has%20released%20several%20videos%20in%20recent%20years%20showing%20some%20of%20the%20objects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20many%20end%20up%20having%20innocent%20explanations%2C%20others%20remain%20shrouded%20in%20mystery%20and%20none%20of%20the%20investigations%20have%20turned%20up%20any%20evidence%20of%20alien%20visitors.%20But%20experts%20continue%20to%20collect%20improved%20data%20about%20the%20objects%2C%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20gaining%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20what%20they%20may%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20search%20for%20alien%20life%20continues%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there's%20no%20evidence%20yet%20that%20aliens%20are%20out%20there%2C%20scientists%20continue%20to%20look%20for%20them.%20With%20every%20mission%20to%20explore%20another%20world%2C%20every%20space%20telescope%20peering%20at%20a%20distant%20star%20system%2C%20and%20every%20radio%20telescope%20listening%20for%20signals%20from%20another%20civilization%2C%20experts%20are%20learning%20more%20about%20the%20Cosmos.%20The%20hunt%20is%20a%20long%20shot%2C%20but%20scientists%20are%20optimistic%20that%20new%20methods%20will%20reveal%20that%20we're%20not%20alone%20in%20the%20universe.%20But%20for%20now%2C%20the%20only%20life%20we%20know%20of%20is%20right%20here%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716644520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F936s70g8_alie