n%20Hyderabad%20and%20(in)%20Delhi%20also%2C%20we%20put%20ourselves%20in%20winning%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20media%20interaction%20after%20their%2036-run%20loss%20to%20SRH.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20you%20have%20streaks.%20RCB%20lost%20almost%20every%20game%20at%20the%20start%20and%20then%20caught%20up.%20That's%20how%20T20%20goes.%20All%20we%20can%20do%20is%20put%20ourselves%20in%20positions%20of%20playoffs%20and%20vying%20for%20finals%2C%20which%20we%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20all%20the%20guys%20throughout%20the%20season%20played%20phenomenal%20cricket.%20There%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20fatigue%20at%20the%20back%20end%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20when%20you're%20in%20games%20like%20this.%20You%20gotta%20turn%20up%20and%20perform.%26quot%3B%20Chasing%20a%20target%20of%20176%2C%20RR%20were%2065%20for%20two%20by%20the%20eighth%20over%2C%20but%20kept%20on%20losing%20wickets%20in%20clusters%20thereafter%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20downfall.%20Commenting%20on%20the%20defeat%2C%C2%A0Sangakkara%C2%A0felt%20the%20middle-order%20could%20have%20done%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20a%20case%20of%20being%20smart%20and%20keeping%20our%20composure.%20Unfortunately%2C%20when%20you%20lose%20wickets%20in%20clusters%2C%20it%20becomes%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20RCB%20chase%2C%20if%20you%20lose%20wickets%2C%20it%20gets%20tense%20and%20close.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20needed%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20from%20our%20middle-order.%26quot%3B%20RR%20were%20also%20without%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jos%20Buttler%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1367-jos-buttler-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJos%20Buttler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20force%20for%20the%20team%20in%20the%20top%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%C2%A0Sangakkara%C2%A0said%20that%20international%20scheduling%20was%20something%20that%20they%20couldn't%20control%2C%20he%20felt%20that%20other%20batters%20should%20have%20stepped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20say%20that%20the%20best%20ability%20is%20availability%2C%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20we%20lost%20Jos.%20He%20is%20a%20big%20loss%2C%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20in%20a%20playoff%20like%20this%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20that%20start%20without%20Jos%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20other%20batters%20to%20also%20step%20up.%26quot%3B%20RR%20have%20a%20few%20players%20travelling%20to%20the%20Americas%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20next%20month%2C%20namely%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Avesh%20Khan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64916-avesh-khan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAvesh%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sanju%20Samson%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1394-yuzvendra-chahal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvesh%20has%20been%20the%20side's%20highest%20wicket-taker%20for%20the%20season%2C%20with%2019%20wickets%20in%2015%20innings%20at%20an%20economy%20of%209.59%2C%20and%C2%A0Sangakkara%C2%A0was%20all-praise%20for%20the%20fast%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20traded%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Devdutt%20Padikkal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110591-devdutt-padikkal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDevdutt%20Padikkal%3C%2Fa%3E%20(to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants)%20for%20Avesh%20because%20we%20knew%20how%20good%20he%20was%2C%20and%20he's%20shown%20that%20throughout%20this%20tournament.%20And%2C%20that's%20why%20he's%20a%20travelling%20reserve%20as%20well%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20for%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20a%20great%20presence%20and%20good%20clarity.%20He's%20very%20good%20at%20finishing%20off%20in%20the%20death.%20I%20think%20he's%20been%20phenomenal%20for%20RR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20we%20couldn't%20ask%20for%20a%20better%20trier.%20He%20bowls%20a%20lot%20in%20training.%20He's%20always%20up%20for%20a%20game.%20I%20thought%20again%20today%20he%20was%20outstanding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20have%20time%20to%20commit%20full-time%20to%20an%20India%20coaching%20job%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangakkara%C2%A0clearly%20refused%20any%20intention%20of%20applying%20for%20the%20India%20head%20coach's%20job%2C%20citing%20time%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20been%20approached%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20commit%20full-time%20to%20an%20India%20coaching%20job.%20Happy%20with%20my%20stint%20with%20Royals%2C%20and%20let's%20see%20how%20it%20goes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716640980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Ftfp77b9g_indian-cricket-team-afp_625x300_29_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-justin-langer-and-ricky-ponting-another-legend-opts-out-of-india-head-coach-job-5743705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kumar%20Sangakkara%20clearly%20refused%20any%20intention%20of%20applying%20for%20the%20India%20head%20coach's%20job%2C%20citing%20time%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafter-justin-langer-and-ricky-ponting-another-legend-opts-out-of-india-head-coach-job-5743705%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcri