nd%20are%20parents%20to%20a%203-year-old%20son%20named%20Agastya%20Pandya%2C%20have%20separated.%20These%20speculations%20were%20triggered%20by%20Natasa%20removing%20the%20'Pandya'%20surname%20from%20her%20Instagram%20handle.%20The%20speculations%20further%20intensified%20when%20a%20post%20titled%20%26quot%3BNatasa%20and%20Hardik%20separated%26quot%3B%20went%20viral%20on%20Reddit%20where%20the%20user%20questioned%20her%20absence%20from%20IPL%202024%20matches%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20she%20has%20not%20posted%20any%20picture%20with%20Hardik%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20The%20post%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20she%20did%20not%20even%20post%20something%20on%20his%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20speculation.%20But%20both%20of%20them%20aren't%20posting%20each%20other%20on%20stories%20(Instagram%20Stories).%20Earlier%2C%20Natasa%20used%20to%20have%20Natasa%20Stankovic%20Pandya%20on%20her%20Instagram%2C%20but%20now%20she%20completely%20removed%20his%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20birthday%20was%20on%204th%20March%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20post%20from%20Hardik%20on%20that%20day%3B%20she%20also%20removed%20all%20recent%20posts%20of%20her%20and%20Hardik%20except%20the%20one%20where%20Agastya%20was%20with%20them.%20Also%2C%20she%20isn't%20seen%20in%20stands%20this%20IPL%20or%20post%20stories%20regarding%20the%20team.%20While%20Krunal%20and%20Pankhuri%20still%20comment%20on%20her%20posts%2C%20something%20is%20definitely%20off%20between%20both%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20rumours%20have%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20nothing%20official%20was%20communicated%20from%20both%20Hardik%20or%20Natasa's%20side.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it%20remains%20nothing%20more%20than%20mere%20speculation%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20Natasa's%20Instagram%20page%2C%20there%20still%20exists%20pictures%20of%20her%20and%20Hardik%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cricketer's%20family.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20reports%20of%20Natasa%20deleting%20all%20pictures%20with%20Hardik%20are%20not%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20had%20a%20disappointing%20IPL%202024%20season%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%20but%20he%20will%20be%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20where%20he%20will%20be%20serving%20as%20the%20vice-captain%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716637320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fg8jidjr8_s_625x300_25_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-natasa-stankovic-why-is-the-celebrity-couple-in-news-5742450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20have%20been%20several%20rumours%20surrounding%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20his%20wife%20Natasa%20Stankovic%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-natasa-stankovic-why-is-the-celebrity-couple-in-news-5742450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-natasa-stankovic-why-is-the-celebrity-couple-in-news-5742450%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhardik-pandya-natasa-stankovic-why-is-the-celebrity-couple-in-news-5742450%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20Singh%20calls%20Deepika%20Padukone%20'Sunshine'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716636998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110422417%2Cimgsize-26334.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-calls-deepika-padukone-sunshine-as-the-pregger-dons-a-stunning-yellow-outfit%2Farticleshow%2F110422425.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%