E%26quot%3BThis%20brings%20upon%20the%20Commission%2C%20a%20higher%20responsibility%20to%20serve%20the%20cause%20of%20electoral%20democracy%20with%20undeterred%20resolution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECommission%20releases%20absolute%20number%20of%20voters%20for%20all%20completed%20phases%20of%20General%20Elections%202024%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDetails%20%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz0QVHGM41Z%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz0QVHGM41Z%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Spokesperson%20ECI%20(%40SpokespersonECI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonECI%2Fstatus%2F1794317350227136897%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20said%20the%20whole%20exercise%20of%20release%20of%20turnout%20data%20from%20the%20day%20elections%20began%20on%20April%2019%20has%20been%20accurate%2C%20consistent%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20election%20laws%20and%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20any%20discrepancy%20whatsoever%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20refuted%20allegations%20about%20delay%20in%20releasing%20voter%20turnout%20data.%20It%20said%20the%20data%20was%20always%20available%2024x7%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bfacilitative%20voter%20turnout%20app%20from%209.30%20am%20on%20the%20polling%20day%20in%20each%20phase%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(app)%20publishes%20estimated%20voter%20turnout%20on%20two%20hourly%20basis%20till%201730%20hours%20(5.30%20pm).%20After%201900%20hours%20(7%20pm)%20when%20the%20polling%20parties%20start%20arriving%2C%20data%20is%20continuously%20updated.%20By%20midnight%20on%20the%20poll%20day%2C%20the%20voter%20turnout%20app%20will%20show%20best%20estimated%20%26quot%3BClose%20of%20Poll%20(COP)%26quot%3B%20data%20in%20percentage%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20media%20organisations%20pick%20up%20data%20at%20different%20points%20in%20time%20as%20per%20their%20convenience%20to%20report%20next%20morning.%20After%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20poll%20parties%2C%20depending%20on%20geographical%20and%20weather%20conditions%2C%20the%20data%20of%20voters%20attains%20finality%20on%20P%2B1%20or%20P%2B2%20or%20P%2B3%20(p%20denotes%20polling%20day)%20or%20more%20days%2C%20depending%20upon%20arrival%20of%20parties%20and%20number%20of%20re-polls%2C%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F735964602%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-XM65tR1OBgrstTNSmuEY%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7729220222793488%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Absolute%20Number%20Of%20Voters%20For%20All%20Completed%20Phases%20%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20of%20the%20turnout%20row%2C%20several%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20the%20Congress's%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20had%20red-flagged%20what%20they%20claimed%20as%20possible%20vote%20fraud%20-%20i.e.%20there%20was%20concern%20the%20increased%20number%20of%20votes%20shown%20after%20polling%20could%20be%20illegally%20added%20to%20the%20tally%20of%20any%20one%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20significantly%2C%20Justices%20S%20Narasimha%20and%20Sanjay%20Karol%20pointed%20out%20the%20interim%20appeal%20by%20the%20petitioner%20-%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20-%20was%20similar%20to%20a%20writ%20petition%20by%20Ms%20Moitra%20in%202019%2C%20which%20wanted%20the%20EC%20to%20%26quot%3Bformulate%20a%20protocol%20mandating%20reporting%20of%20Form%2017C...%20within%2048%20hours%20(for%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election)%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20is%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20nexus%20between%202019%20and%202024%20applications%3F%20Why%20didn't%20you%20file%20a%20separate%20writ%20petition%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20questioned%20ADR%2C%20insisting%20it%20would%20not%20intervene%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20election.%20%26quot%3BThis%20application%20will%20be%20heard%20after%20the%20election...%20in-between%20an%20election%2C%20hands%20off.%20We%20cannot%20interrupt%20(the%20electoral%20process)...%20we%20are%20also%20responsible%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Datta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716636660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F83p3bka_election-generic-reuters_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnobody-can-change-data-of-votes-polled-says-poll-body-notes-pattern-of-false-narratives-5743166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20today%20released%20the%20absolute%20number%20of%20voters%20for%20all%20the%20completed%20phases%20-%20six%20of%20the%20seven%20phases%20-%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnobody-can-change-data-of-votes-polled-says-poll-body-notes-pattern-of-false-narratives-5743166%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnobody-can-change-data-of-votes-polled-says-poll-body-notes-pattern-of-false-narratives-5743166%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnobody-can-change-data-of-votes-polled-says-poll-body-notes-pattern-of-false-narratives-5743166%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20Punjab%20government%20approves%20registration%20of%20more%20cases%20against%20Imran%20Khan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716635840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110422000%2Cimgsize-24226.cms%22%2C%22originI