%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donkey%20milk%2C%20which%20has%20little%20value%20in%20India%2C%20has%20made%20Dhiren%20Solanki%20a%20successful%20farmer%20in%20Gujarat.%20He%20tapped%20into%20its%20international%20demand%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20and%20cosmetics%20industry%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20business%20within%20two%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350485%2Fdonkey-milk-farming-value-in-india-gujarat-farmer-earns-lakhs-by-selling-nutritious-donkey-milk-powder%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20%E2%80%98MBA%20Sarpanch%E2%80%99%20Who%20Kept%20All%20Her%20Promises%20%26amp%3B%20Brought%20Water%2C%20Roads%20%26amp%3B%20Education%20to%20a%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20lies%20a%20road%20in%20the%20main%20bazaar%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20Soda%20village%20of%20Rajasthan.%20At%20first%20glance%2C%20it%20may%20seem%20like%20an%20ordinary%20village%20street%2C%20but%20the%20locals%20see%20it%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20progress.%20As%20I%20get%20on%20a%20call%20with%20Ladu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20steady%20sound%20of%20trucks%2C%20cars%2C%20bullock%20carts%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20bicycles%20ploughing%20through%20the%20street%20eclipse%20most%20of%20his%20words.%20He%20shouts%20over%20the%20din%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20trucks%20can%20drive%20on%20this%20road!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadu%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20why%20this%20is%20a%20miracle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20even%20two%20bicycles%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pass%20simultaneously.%20What%20else%20can%20you%20expect%20from%20a%20two-foot-wide%20road%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks.%20I%20agree.%20So%2C%20naturally%2C%20watching%20the%20path%20accommodating%20trucks%20and%20lorries%20is