riving%20water%20body%20that%20provides%20for%20the%20village's%20water%20needs%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsarpanch-3-1715863199.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsarpanch-3-1715863199-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsarpanch-3-1715863199-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsarpanch-3-1715863199-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsarpanch-3-1715863199-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350285%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERajawat%20has%20transformed%20the%20reservoir%20into%20a%20thriving%20water%20body%20that%20provides%20for%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20water%20needs%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chhavi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETracing%20back%20to%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309116%2Fias-officer-anshul-gupta-efi-volunteers-restore-pond-wildlife-ujjain-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20shape%2C%20Rajawat%20says%20it%20was%20the%20drought%20of%202009%20that%20was%20the%20precursor.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20droughts%20the%20village%20had%20experienced.%20Our%20animals%20were%20dying%2C%20there%20was%20no%20fodder%20and%20people%20were%20consuming%20the%20groundwater%2C%20which%20had%20been%20declared%20unsafe%20for%20anything%2C%20even%20irrigation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20blame%20them.%20How%20else%20would%20they%20survive%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tense%20time.%20During%20this%20unimaginable%20hardship%2C%20Rajawat%20taking%20charge%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpan